comments: Horford (BOS) makes incidental contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) grabs Horford (BOS) and affects his FOM as he is trying to advance up the court.
Holiday (MIL) reaches in and makes contact to Brown's (BOS) arm as he gathers that affects his driving shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) jumps in front of and to the side of Holiday (MIL) as he contests the jump shot attempt.  The marginal contact is created by Holiday extending his leg.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly has an arm placed around Horford's (BOS) front during the rebound but the contact is marginal.  Incidental contact then occurs as both players reach for the loose ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) does not have full control of the ball as he receives the pass in the paint and does not travel upon controlling the ball.
After initially making contact with the ball, Brown (BOS) makes contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Antetokounmpo's (MIL) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim and the shot clock expires.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Williams (BOS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Holiday (MIL) does not release the throw-in within five seconds.
Smart (BOS) places his hand on Antetokounmpo's (MIL) left arm as he elevates for the shot attempt but the contact is marginal and does not affect his shot attempt.
Antetokounpo (MIL) jumps along with Brown (BOS) and absorbs the contact to his front as the two players meet at the basket.
Horford (BOS) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.

Holiday (MIL) places his off-arm against Tatum (BOS) and the two players make incidental foot to foot contact that causes Tatum to lose his balance.  Holiday does not extend his arm into Tatum or otherwise dislodge him from his defensive position.
As Tatum (BOS) is falling to the floor, he grabs Holiday's (MIL) arm and causes him to lose control of his dribble.
Holiday (MIL) commits a foul by making contact with Smart's (BOS) arms before he is bringing the ball upward toward the basket.  A personal foul is correctly called.
Portis (MIL) makes marginal contact with Smart (BOS) as he reaches for the rebound but does not affect Smart's ability to control the ball.

Portis (MIL), Williams (BOS), and Lopez (MIL) make incidental contact with each other as they reach for the rebound.  Williams III (BOS) then makes contact with the ball and deflects it off of the backboard.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is confirmed that Horford (BOS) does not release the tip-in shot before the expiration of the game clock and the basket is not counted.
